  "detailed_description": "Gun Mage is a fast-paced, action-packed, 2D Combat-Platformer game where you only have one bullet in the chamber of your weapon. And you’re gonna have to make it count.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChallenge your friends online (with the steam remote together) or on the comfort of your couch in an epic gun duel to the death ! Jump, shoot, reflect and bluff your way up to the top and become the ultimate Gun Mage !",
  "about_the_game": "Gun Mage is a fast-paced, action-packed, 2D Combat-Platformer game where you only have one bullet in the chamber of your weapon. And you’re gonna have to make it count.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChallenge your friends online (with the steam remote together) or on the comfort of your couch in an epic gun duel to the death ! Jump, shoot, reflect and bluff your way up to the top and become the ultimate Gun Mage !",
